To run phpipam in Docker for development purposes:

1. Install Docker & Docker Compose
2. `docker-compose up`
3. Go to http://localhost:8081/
4. Choose "New Installation"
5. Choose "Automatic"
6. Enter "phpipam" as both the MySQL username and password
7. Press the "Advanced Options" button and deselect all the checkboxes
8. Proceed through the rest of the installation process
